OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector David Butt spoke
OL,8,Foutside Merthyr Crown Court following
OL,9,Fthe sentencing
OL,11,FA former hospital worker and her
OL,12,Fpartner have been jailed for planning
OL,13,Fthe "brutal" sexual assault of young
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FTracy Turner, 52 and Stuart Compton,
OL,17,F46, sent each other thousands of
OL,18,Fmessages planning the depraved abuse
OL,19,Fof two girls and a boy.
