OL,6,FMerthyr Crown Court heard the couple's
OL,7,Fplan failed after an online dating app
OL,8,Finformed police of concerns about
OL,9,FCompton. The pair where then arrested.
OL,11,FAt an earlier hearing, the couple, who
OL,12,Freferred to each other as Bonnie and
OL,13,FClyde, both pleaded guilty to six
OL,14,Fcounts of arranging sex with a child.
OL,16,FCompton also pleaded guilty to six
OL,17,Fcounts of making indecent images, and
OL,18,FTurner, who who worked as an operating
OL,19,Ftheatre assistant in Cardiff, admitted
OL,20,Ftwo counts of the same offence.
